{"content":"<blockquote>\n<p><strong>Tips</strong>: VueRouter 是Vue官方为单应用专门打造的。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>接下来看看如何安装<code v-pre>VueRouter</code>。</p>\n<p>分别有使用<code v-pre>CDN</code>引入和使用<code v-pre>NPM</code>安装两种方式。</p>\n<CodeTabs id=\"11\" :data='[{\"id\":\"CDN\"},{\"id\":\"NPM\"}]'><template #title0=\"{ value, isActive }\"><span>CDN</span></template><template #title1=\"{ value, isActive }\"><VPIcon name=\"logos:npm-icon\"/><span>NPM</span></template><template #tab0=\"{ value, isActive }\"><div class=\"language-sh line-numbers-mode\" data-ext=\"sh\" data-title=\"sh\"><button class=\"copy\" title=\"复制代码\" data-copied=\"已复制\"></button><pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark vp-code\" v-pre=\"\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">https://unpkg.com/vue-router@2.0.0/dist/vue-router.js</span></span></code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"line-numbers\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"counter-reset:line-number 0\"><div class=\"line-number\"></div></div></div></template><template #tab1=\"{ value, isActive }\"><div class=\"language-sh line-numbers-mode\" data-ext=\"sh\" data-title=\"sh\"><button class=\"copy\" title=\"复制代码\" data-copied=\"已复制\"></button><pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark vp-code\" v-pre=\"\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">npm</span><span class=\"space\"> </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">install</span><span class=\"space\"> </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">vue-router@4</span></span></code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"line-numbers\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"counter-reset:line-number 0\"><div class=\"line-number\"></div></div></div></template></CodeTabs><p>这里采用CDN的方式。</p>\n<p>其基本的使用方法是：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>使用<code v-pre>router-link</code>组件来导航，通过<code v-pre>to</code>来跳转指定链接（相当于<code v-pre>&lt;a&gt; &lt;/a&gt;</code>标签）。</li>\n<li>使用<code v-pre>router-view</code>组件定义路由出口，路由匹